entities.createSql: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`meanings` TEXT, `word` TEXT NOT NULL, `wordsetId` TEXT NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY(`wordsetId`))

contentSyncTriggers: CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_dictionary_table_fts_BEFORE_UPDATE BEFORE UPDATE ON `dictionary_table` BEGIN DELETE FROM `dictionary_table_fts` WHERE `docid`=OLD.`rowid`; END
CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_dictionary_table_fts_BEFORE_DELETE BEFORE DELETE ON `dictionary_table` BEGIN DELETE FROM `dictionary_table_fts` WHERE `docid`=OLD.`rowid`; END

CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_dictionary_table_fts_AFTER_UPDATE AFTER UPDATE ON `dictionary_table` BEGIN INSERT INTO `dictionary_table_fts`(`docid`, `meanings`, `word`, `wordsetId`) VALUES (NEW.`rowid`, NEW.`meanings`, NEW.`word`, NEW.`wordsetId`); END

CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_dictionary_table_fts_AFTER_INSERT AFTER INSERT ON `dictionary_table` BEGIN INSERT INTO `dictionary_table_fts`(`docid`, `meanings`, `word`, `wordsetId`) VALUES (NEW.`rowid`, NEW.`meanings`, NEW.`word`, NEW.`wordsetId`); END
entities.createSql: CREATE VIRTUAL TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` USING FTS4(`meanings` TEXT, `word` TEXT NOT NULL, `wordsetId` TEXT NOT NULL, content=`dictionary_table`)
